<p>Hello,</p>
<p>{{ .InviterName }} invited you to join project <strong>{{ .ProjectName }}</strong> as <strong>{{ .Role }}</strong>.</p>
{{ if .ExpiresAt }}<p>This invitation expires on {{ .ExpiresAt }}.</p>{{ end }}
<p><strong>Invitation token:</strong> <code>{{ .Token }}</code></p>
{{ if .AcceptURL }}<p>You can also accept directly by visiting: <a href="{{ .AcceptURL }}">Accept Invitation</a></p>{{ end }}
<p>Please log in to Semaphore at <a href="{{ .WebURL }}">{{ .WebURL }}</a> and use the token above to accept the invitation.</p>

